        ]
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "highlight",
      "content": "Best practice: Measure UVI at the basking surface with a Solarmeter 6.5 and adjust distance to reach 4.5-6.0."
    },
    {
      "type": "section",
      "heading": "Full-Spectrum Illumination"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "content": "Bright visible light improves activity and appetite. Use a 6500K LED bar that covers most of the enclosure length."
